Name: qec
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2026-05-14
Author: Sid Richards
Maintainer: Sid Richards
Title: Quantum Error Correction
Description: Educational MATLAB/Octave implementations of quantum error-correction codes, syndrome decoders, and code-capacity Monte Carlo simulations. Includes repetition, [[4,2,2]], Shor, Steane, five-qubit, color, Bacon-Shor, and surface-layout examples.
Categories: Education, Science, Quantum Computing
Depends: octave (>= 6.0.0)
License: MIT
Url: https://github.com/SidRichardsQuantum/Quantum_Error_Correction
